# API Examples for Dashboard Backend
# Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Get All Users
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users

### Get Users with Pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users?page=1&limit=5

### Get Users with Search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users?search=john

### Get User Statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/stats

### Create User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "role": "USER"
}

### Create Admin User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin User",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

